pages.title: In Minecraft
pages.text: A dark oak is a tree with dark bark and wood. It is a dark variant of the oak. Dark oaks have thick trunks and are found in the dark forest biome.

pages.title: On Earth
pages.text: Oaks are important components of hardwood forests; some species grow in associations with members of the Ericaceae in oakâ€“heath forests. Fossil oaks date back to the Middle Eocene. In culture, the oak tree is a symbol of strength and serves as the national tree of many countries.
